        "text": "Task Forces were silent again today. Cominch in 021615 (Aidac) directed that Comtaskfor 11 use his combined forces to make an attack in the New Britaln - Solomon Area about March lOth. Task Force 11 would then return to Pearl if directed by Cincpac. To obtain full-use of fuel available Cincpac sent despatches 030935 and 031007 (filed with orders). The situation at Canton was unreported today. An attempt to float the TAYLOR was supposed -to have been made.",
        "degraded": true
