        "text": "The CALIFORNIA was placed in drydock. The press reports the fall of Bataan defenders, but Corregidor still holds. Thus any relief to that area from here cannot be undertaken. f.h. ... ,, d1.· · i,o·.. ....~ ?\\ ~ ,. ., ~ Vice Admiral Glassford is enroute Pearl from Sydney by air.",
