        "text": "CinCPac 190839 Rear Admiral McCain becomes Comairsopac. Fletcher will arrive Pearl about May 28th. Colonel Clements USMC, who got out of Corrigedor April lOth gave a gloomy talk on how we lost the Philippines. Aside from small scale air activity the Southwest Pacific seems quiet.",
