        "text": "TF 1 is enroute the HAWAIIAN area for training with TF 17. Cincpac 050601 recommends on LIONS, OAKS, and construction battalions for the South Pacific. Satisfactory arrangements have been made for censorship of British radio stations at CA10N, CHRIS~~s, and FANNING. There is still no word from the ESSO LITTLE ROCK. That tanker is now overdue at NOUMEA three days.",
